title: MuscleTech Mass Gainer was uniquely pure.
pid: 7898594f-b826-4d25-8ae0-6d53219251a9
body: |2-
  Consumer Reports in 2025 tested studied 23 protein brands.
  It was the only one without any detectable lead.
  Some had on the order of a thousand times
  some important authority's 'acceptable' level.
